                            <h3>Special requirements</h3>
                            <div class="text-wrap">
                                <p>I would like to book a twin room with a definite sea view please. Thank you and kind regards, John Livingston</p>
                            </div>

                            <h3>Payment</h3>
                            <div class="text-wrap">
